Interface IVisitable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AndNode, EqOperation, ExprNode, GenericNode, GenericOperation, GeOperation, GtOperation, LeOperation, LtOperation, NeOperation, OperandNode, OrNode

    public interface IVisitable
    IVisitable interface is used to mark a class as visitable. Each visitable class should have an accept() method.

    razvan
